<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Movies | Cineverse 🎬</title>

    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #0d0d0d;
            color: white;
        }

        header {
            background: #111;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        header h1 {
            color: #ff3c3c;
        }

        nav a {
            color: white;
            margin-left: 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: #ff3c3c;
        }

        .section {
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .movies {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 30px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .movie-card {
            background: #1a1a1a;
            border-radius: 10px;
            width: 300px;
            padding: 15px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .movie-card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .movie-card img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .movie-card h3 {
            margin-top: 10px;
            color: #ff3c3c;
        }

        .movie-card p {
            color: #ccc;
        }

        footer {
            background: #111;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <h1>Cineverse 🎬</h1>
    <nav>
        <a href="index.html">Home</a>
        <a href="#">Movies</a>
        <a href="#">Universes</a>
        <a href="#">About</a>
    </nav>
</header>

<section class="section">
    <h2>🎥 Our Movies</h2>

    <div class="movies">

        <!-- Movie 1 -->
        <div class="movie-card">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x180">
            <h3>The Pralay Begins - Part 1</h3>
            <p>The beginning of destruction and chaos in the universe. A new era starts here.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Movie 2 -->
        <div class="movie-card">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x180">
            <h3>The Pralay Begins - Part 2</h3>
            <p>The story continues as the universe faces greater threats and unexpected twists.</p>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<footer>
    <p>© 2026 Cineverse | All Rights Reserved 🚀</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
